msgstr "Quantity to adjust. POSITIVE adds to stock, NEGATIVE subtracts. Filament in grams, aggregate in units. E.g. 500 adds 500 g; -200 removes 200 g. If you want to set stock to an exact value, check how much there is today and enter the difference."

msgid "Motivo del ajuste (ej: conteo físico, rotura, sobrante de impresión, carga inicial de stock)."
msgstr "Reason for the adjustment (e.g. physical count, breakage, print surplus, initial stock load)."

msgid "Elegí exactamente un artículo: un Filamento o un Agregado (no ambos, no ninguno)."
msgstr "Choose exactly one item: a Filament or an Aggregate (not both, not neither)."

msgid "Ingresá una cantidad distinta de cero."
msgstr "Enter a non-zero quantity."

