msgstr "Set when an approved order is cancelled: the material of what was not printed, the parts and the add-ons have already been returned to stock. Prevents returning twice."

msgid "Sumado al stock de terminados"
msgstr "Added to finished stock"

msgid "Se marca al completar un pedido 'para stock': ya se sumaron sus unidades terminadas al stock de productos. Evita sumar dos veces."
msgstr "Set when a 'for stock' order is completed: its finished units have already been added to the products stock. Prevents adding twice."

msgid "No se puede aprobar el presupuesto #%(pk)s: su estado es '%(status)s'. Solo se pueden aprobar presupuestos en estado Borrador o Enviado."
msgstr "Budget #%(pk)s cannot be approved: its status is '%(status)s'. Only budgets in Draft or Sent status can be approved."

